Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:02.86,mianze,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}翻譯:小呆&うんこマン  時間:希梅亞（神奇的qd 修）  後期:火貓少女  MKV:烏賊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得最近很熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說夏天了 連梅雨季都還沒到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心一年四季都是火熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.08,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,學園七恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又想到什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙吾 你應該更有餘裕點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊繃的線一刀就能輕易斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 要斬斷隨風而動的線是極其困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到了一項可以讓你放鬆享受的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內容是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,納涼試膽大會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠不合時宜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:00:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個應該不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在我所知的鬼故事裡 有人被殺很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在深夜敲校舍二樓女廁所右起第二扇門…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你是想穿紅外套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是藍外套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者是黃外套呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答紅外套 就會渾身浴血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答藍外套 就會被抽乾血液 渾身鐵青
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃…黃色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃色?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被逼吃下大量香蕉 全身泛黃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一回 Little Busters試膽 恐怖·NO·RYO大會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 請鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問 試膽是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫醬 就是那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣用錐子在指縫間…扎扎扎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩這個嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到我藏在校舍各樓層的四張符紙後返回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終點就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 感覺好真格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先分組吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 和理樹分開了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 大姐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那畫到A的鈴隊來打頭陣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可怕 不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Call me for helper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有貝爾加和斯特萊爾加在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒什麼可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 共赴校舍吧 內匠頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:05.04,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}※內匠頭 古時日本官名 是管內匠寮的長官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們不打算跟來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風紀委員們教過牠們不能進校舍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 貝爾加 斯特萊爾加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好多貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們和狗不同 是不聽人話的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 三個人一起我就不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怕了 鈴醬和庫醬也就不害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一組 差不多該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 理樹 和我們一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭著肩 蹦蹦跳跳地上路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就跟被帶走的外星人似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一處是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們待在這裡 我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼知道那個白癡老哥搞的什麼花樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好 我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同學太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬醬掛了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的慘叫其實是和Fear雙關的…搞笑Shout嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別死 活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有脈搏 別放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎有人中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面說第一張符紙在恭介的教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介的教室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡走快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擋道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 小把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉頰好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是臉頰魔人幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽穴怪人也是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃外套!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我比較快…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃色的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 大姐頭好像很享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆似乎不怎麼怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「呀 好怕怕哦 理樹君」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…你很遺憾沒出現這種局面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 當然不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這被詛咒的旋律是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是舊式收錄音機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這尖銳的視線是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是反光的一圓硬幣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斷…斷手!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來以前發生過叫斷手拉麵的案子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是灌滿了番茄醬的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 往裡面加點滑溜菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓濕滑的指尖剛好能夠到後頸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下理科室了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是唯姐 真可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年 從這裡起就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在你們身後悠閒地觀賞你們受驚時的舉動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也太殘忍了啦 大姐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…能走慢點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你不還不怕的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 走在唯姐身後 我連揍飛總統的自信都有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過其實還是會怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君看來不怎麼怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒不是 我也挺怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然大家都會害怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突…突然有陣寒意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是風?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是先讓…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 唯姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L…Let's search的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鈴她們?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬醬 小毬醬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別死 活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\K80\pos(460,389)\fs30\bord0}沒有反應。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\K130\pos(630,433)\fs30\bord0}看來死透了。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是小毬Max 竟然真的暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛突然出來嚇人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何不可 大家都是女孩子 看看又不會懷孕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個問題啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好工口的叫醒方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然消失就是跑來幹這種勾當的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入負責嚇唬你們的一方比較有意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們收集了幾張符紙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 大豐收啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你們倆…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣Go straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在我的肌肉裡睡的正香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個待在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫公交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也發現了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 偷偷摸摸地窺探我們半天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特 庫特!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「納涼」不成 引來「怨靈」了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(288,437)}NO-RYO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(533,437)}ON-RYO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥? 怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼情況!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 是理樹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怨靈?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:37.97,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,對方不在服務區內或已關機 目前無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不通…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是恭介的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道會有人想落跑 事先設好了金屬盆陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是恭介的手法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別玩手電筒了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 你的肌肉贏得了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怨靈?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特說她感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試膽大會中止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在起 開始驅逐怨靈!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怨靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是想到什麼做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現況的確難以置信 但卻無法視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹 幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:16:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去 和鈴醬一起就不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前來助陣!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 任務開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在一樓 完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到 完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撒!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在二樓 包抄它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們真的抓得到那貨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗學長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找來了強力幫手 哼!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西園 怨靈該怎麼抓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多一事不如少一事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經深陷其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有沒有什麼弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈異生物一般都懼怕強大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喧囂的場所 亮光它們應該也怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情大條了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可興奮著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三樓 無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪在發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請小心 它就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來保護西園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡靈退散 惡靈退散
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退散 退散 退散
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴君 小毬君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它來了 鈴醬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼先生 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小毬醬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能叫它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你們那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳥…先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好壯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼 滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別往裡加滑溜菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這鳥是小皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小皮!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我以前從北海道旅遊歸來時有隻白頭海雕的寶寶很親近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給牠取名為小皮 很是疼愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 我們還和牠一起玩耍過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠對我倒是不理不睬的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 白頭海雕是不能家養的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就忍痛把小皮送回了北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠難道是來見恭介的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小皮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小皮 要再來玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來一切都歸咎於恭介氏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 不是怨靈就最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 任務完成!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 這一晚過的真是痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是最後抵達的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你們倆去哪兒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好意思說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校長室裡的陷阱拖住了我們好半天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要搞那麼逼真嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的臉怎麼青了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就沒碰過那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這玩意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好…趕快燒掉它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1100)\bord1\1a&HFF&\3a&H1F&\3c&HE33D13&\pos(425,370)\blur3\be11\t(9300,9300,\\3a&HFF&)}第11話\N恐怖·NO·RYO大會
