Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1100)\bord0\pos(425,370)\blur1\t(9300,10000,\rnd17\blur5)\t(10000,11000,\rnd30}第11話\N恐怖·NO·RYO大會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1100)\bord0\pos(425,370)\blur1\t(9300,10000,\rnd17\blur5)\t(10000,11000,\rnd30)}第11話\N恐怖·NO·RYO大會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西園同學總是遠望著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹想把西園拉入Little Busters嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 讓她成為我們的夥伴
